{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"alias":"illegal-condemned-cockatiel","creation_channel":"cli","description":"## Description\nDocument the new surface so clients can adopt it: the optional `[metrics]` extra + external-CLI prerequisites (scc/jscpd), the `[code_health]` config keys, the analyzer/adapter set, and the hard Unavailable fallback contract. Update reuse-surface (the metrics section) and user-guide (the Metrics section).\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- [ ] docs/reuse-surface.md metrics section documents the analyzer seam + the [metrics] extra + external CLIs.\n- [ ] docs/user-guide.md Metrics section documents config keys, tool prerequisites, and the \"no analyzer -> Unavailable\" behavior.\n- [ ] AGENTS.md metrics pointer updated if the one-line description changed.\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] tests/scripts/test_metrics_docs.py (or equivalent) passes; docs build/lint clean.\n\n## Dependencies: Child 7 (final shape)\n## Files likely touched: docs/reuse-surface.md, docs/user-guide.md, AGENTS.md\n## Estimated scope: S-M","id":"a9dd-041f-de89-48c5","parent_id":"839b-f6d2-7e1a-4051","priority":2,"tags":["metrics","code-health"],"ticket_type":"task","title":"Docs: the [metrics] extra, [code_health] config, adapter set, and the fallback contract"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1784517478186894001,"uuid":"c0a65224-420a-488a-955a-72152f2e2fd9"}